Summary:
Implemented a pattern-matching based expression equivalence validator for Module 1 algebraic expressions.

Changes:
- Created lib/activities/algebraic/equivalence.ts (489 lines)
- Created __tests__/lib/activities/algebraic/equivalence.test.ts (266 lines)

Key Features:
- checkEquivalence() function for comparing algebraic expressions
- normalizeExpression() helper for standardizing expressions
- Polynomial equivalence: factored vs expanded forms (x+a)(x+b) ↔ x^2+(a+b)x+ab
- Complex number equivalence: handles a+bi, bi+a, a-bi forms
- Fraction equivalence: handles a/b, mixed numbers, fraction addition
- Radical equivalence: handles √n, n√a, cube roots (³√n), radical addition
- Rearranged terms: handles commutative property of addition

Test Results:
